snippet.title: Rebuild 3: Gangs of Deadsville Official Trailer HD
snippet.description:
Now on Steam, GOG and http://rebuildgame.com. Rebuild a city destroyed by the zombie apocalypse in this indie strategy / simulation game by Sarah Northway.

Coming soon to iOS and Android!
